please understand that

00:11:18.890 --> 00:11:21.190
just because something
looks accessible

00:11:21.190 --> 00:11:26.270
to you does not mean it is
accessible to screen reader users.

00:11:28.320 --> 00:11:32.690
This is why there is a huge
difference between automated testing

00:11:32.690 --> 00:11:33.690
and manual testing.

00:11:34.780 --> 00:11:39.190
